    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "@iam4x agree that's an easy fix, we have the same strategy in [React InstantSearch](https://github.com/algolia/react-instantsearch/blob/7c19c75df4856a3e5afe3c79fc9dee470d956633/packages/react-instantsearch/src/core/createWidgetsManager.js#L15-L18). But we should not rely on that since it's not predictable at all. For example, in React when they will launch the async rendering the lib could cause multiple request because of that. We should find a proper API to handle this case, it's a recurring problem.",
