    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "How can we handle both “yes we want a new request if a widget is unmourned, but none if we’re also going to delete everything”. Maybe requestIdleCallback, but that doesn’t work in node. All I can think of is that we need to have a queue that must be flushed, but I can’t think of an implementation without timers ",
